{"tid":1191420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登俾人話細路哥論壇 原因係個正負評制度","createTime":"2019-06-08T02:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T14:19:00.000Z","uid":190817,"like":101,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"94cc3ca9a12819980823c9e23a0bf53f2ac069b8","tid":1191420,"uid":190817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:03:16.000Z","msg":"ADMIN快手Del左個正負評制度啦 <br />\n呢個制度完全害鳩死人 尤其依家69遊行<br />\n<br />\n好多Post 亂鳩咁UP 明明成篇歪理 都一大堆正評<br />\n乜野警犬係FD 乜野End game <br />\n好多小朋友總之見到你打一大篇野 <br />\n無論岩定錯 就會留正評 正評數一多<br />\n之後其他小朋友見到以為好野 睇都唔睇就跟住留<br />\n<br />\n呢個機制下 五毛，三毛就最開心<br />\n以前高登時 佢地要不停係唔同PO回覆先可以帶風向<br />\n依家輕鬆又方便 叫一班人集中正/負評 一個內容 就搞掂 <br />\n隨時個數字ADMIN 有份改 之前都試過啦 同英皇賣廣告個d特別多正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正班連登仔無乜獨立思考能力 淨係識圍繞住正負評數量特別多的內容討論 正/負評數量一多就信<br />\n有時往往有意義的內容/指正錯誤的內容就係因為無人留評 就WFC <br />\n好多人只會睇評價最多的內容..."},{"pid":"b1ac4deb8bd709c7ac45d1cca5f03cf45951a359","tid":1191420,"uid":249885,"like":13,"dislike":13,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"連登最多牙蘇狗 無分析力 等呢班賤種俾人玩弄下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900d6ed8660046a82f29890dca2a21f9806a4ebb","tid":1191420,"uid":190817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b1ac4deb8bd709c7ac45d1cca5f03cf45951a359","tid":1191420,"uid":249885,"like":13,"dislike":13,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:04:29.000Z","msg":"連登最多牙蘇狗 無分析力 等呢班賤種俾人玩弄下都好<img src=\"/assets/faces